e time use buckwheat flour and omit the first step.","Buckwheat grain is also known as buckwheat groats.","Either brown or white buckwheat can be used in this recipe, keep in mind brown grain will make Blinis brown in color.","Serve Blinis with sour cream and caviar or smoked salmon, melted butter, jelly or preserves."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h 30m","20 pieces"]}